{"id": "1440631823192428564", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：原初宿命之战 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战**\n荒诞与混沌的梦境伊始之初，祂就注定会面对祂的宿命。\n但祂已经历了太多，也定义了太多。\n祂已决意以人类能够保持的最大理智，注视自己的起源，那至高的神祇。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"War of Primordial Destiny\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: War of Primordial Destiny**\nFrom the very beginning of the absurd and chaotic dream, They were destined to confront Their fate.\nYet They have experienced too much, and defined too much.\nThey have resolved, with the maximum sanity a human can retain, to gaze upon Their own origin: The Supreme Will.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:16:32.294000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1440631823603601440", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 901332, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440631823603601440/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69cce270&is=69cb90f0&hm=84927b7e155b08b196ed3f72e8858ab278381612ec96419577c9c4225eefe3cb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440632686577451028", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 一位至珍者之死-Death of the Beloved-**\n\n疯狂，毁灭的前奏，这是有序世界的底层逻辑。\n祂会毁灭吗，世界会毁灭吗？\n无人知晓。\n但创世神面前，疯狂正在滋养出祂与世界的新生。\n\nMadness, the prelude to destruction, is the underlying logic of the ordered world.\nWill It perish? Will the world be destroyed?\nNo one knows.\nBut before the Creator, madness is fostering the rebirth of Them and the world.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:19:58.141000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440632686002569247", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 822942, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440632686002569247/1.jpg?ex=69cce33e&is=69cb91be&hm=ddf1ba5896481a8eef55c71dfb8418ee019e098c627b1a63fa5e7dcc2dc77ad9&"}, {"id": "1440632686317146162", "filename": "01._-Death_of_the_Beloved-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 48800834, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440632686317146162/01._-Death_of_the_Beloved-.wav?ex=69cce33e&is=69cb91be&hm=32be4de38b316e535c27dcb42bd73b8fd89e856cf2bd44c2902f59a7de58eec7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440632803778756698", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 疯狂赋格-Fugue of Madness-**\n\n疯狂，毁灭的前奏，这是有序世界的底层逻辑。\n祂会毁灭吗，世界会毁灭吗？\n无人知晓。\n但创世神面前，疯狂正在滋养出祂与世界的新生。\n\nMadness, the prelude to destruction, is the underlying logic of the ordered world.\nWill It perish? Will the world be destroyed?\nNo one knows.\nBut before the Creator, madness is fostering the rebirth of Them and the world.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:20:26.084000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-25T04:13:37.592000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440632802654687233", "filename": "02._-Fugue_of_Madness-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 42185176, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440632802654687233/02._-Fugue_of_Madness-.wav?ex=69cce359&is=69cb91d9&hm=9cf5149090c04c04f3437e3bad7f02a5d5ba98d5a75e08a97a349c8722d8e2fb&"}, {"id": "1440632803086569565", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 829194, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440632803086569565/2.jpg?ex=69cce359&is=69cb91d9&hm=98adeef79b3aa7e8da9409686a1ea991e03fa7888db968c98d2916f714716b02&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440632897433243649", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 多重性战歌-Battle Hymn-**\n\n战士、复仇者、奴隶、主人、商人。\n相同的立场？不同的立场？相同的立场。\n\nWarrior. Avenger. Slave. Master. Merchant.\nSame stance? Different stances? The same stance.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:20:48.413000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:21:55.142000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440632896414290001", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 826886, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440632896414290001/3.jpg?ex=69cce370&is=69cb91f0&hm=723a995874f278c6b2db23b1b2b866e8fa608104020161f7eba0ec48a5bea5fc&"}, {"id": "1440632896900698182", "filename": "03._-Battle_Hymn-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 50598004, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440632896900698182/03._-Battle_Hymn-.wav?ex=69cce370&is=69cb91f0&hm=17494d5e75912c8be78e4799794d852fae9d5c7d5a2da019d23dcc0975d5fa7e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440633092082761781", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 常世颂-Ode to the Mundane-**\n\n我们或许是亘古中的转瞬，狂流中的砂砾。\n然而常世便是我们珍贵的永恒，因为无论世界如何疯狂混乱——\n人类的尊严，会建立于理性的光辉之上。\n\nWe may be fleeting moments in eternity, grains of sand in a raging torrent.\nYet our precious eternity lies in this mundane world, for no matter how mad and chaotic the world becomes—\nhuman dignity shall be built upon the radiance of reason.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:21:34.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440633091499626648", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 813694, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633091499626648/4.jpg?ex=69cce39e&is=69cb921e&hm=a8ce4736d5427d4b507a33d20c411b3ac7fdd607c920720ae31b6eecadf9148a&"}, {"id": "1440633091809869925", "filename": "04._-Ode_to_the_Mundane-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 3103807, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633091809869925/04._-Ode_to_the_Mundane-.mp3?ex=69cce39e&is=69cb921e&hm=8207c56daaa436882ce5febafdf3a70893f8ad94438a736037b0a2c539ca7455&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440633639942492190", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05. 向创世神扬帆-Sail to the Creator-**\n\n她们围绕着你，她们敬慕着你，她们陪伴着你。\n她们向创世神扬帆。\n\nThey surround you, they revere you, they accompany you.\nThey set sail toward the Creator.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:23:45.441000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440633639095242862", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 825807, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633639095242862/5.jpg?ex=69cce421&is=69cb92a1&hm=eeb2aacce706edeb8c0ea23ab7c11593e03943de318d5722dda4bad233ec8d14&"}, {"id": "1440633639502217288", "filename": "05._-Sail_to_the_Creator-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 47512792, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633639502217288/05._-Sail_to_the_Creator-.wav?ex=69cce421&is=69cb92a1&hm=f99ee1c9f4bf1125c2cf1fb735a3d3d516692032ae2b8940a5b2a42d587df905&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440633746469683273", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07. 唯一的终局-The Only Finale-**\n\n祂们的可能性线条，分离、收束、崩散。\n直到迎来了唯一的救世主，直到终于迈入了唯一的终局。\n\nThe possibility threads of Them diverged, converged, and scattered.\nUntil the one and only savior arrived, until They finally stepped into the one and only finale.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:24:10.839000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440633745957982340", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 822276, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633745957982340/7.jpg?ex=69cce43a&is=69cb92ba&hm=f53d50865bc9512652df568cea013834320f68eb17cca8e6fb51e8442508d672&"}, {"id": "1440633746217898014", "filename": "07._-The_Only_Finale-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 3357091, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633746217898014/07._-The_Only_Finale-.mp3?ex=69cce43a&is=69cb92ba&hm=48fcc9ff1f85047ab4c22a84d6589c765471ff2ce7da557545ba05a85d08c196&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440633762194001952", "channel_id": "1440631823192428564", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06. 敌人，友人-Foe, Friend-**\n\n一个完整的传奇不能缺少化敌为友。\n\nNo complete legend is without foes turned friends.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:24:14.588000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🩷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "stone", "emoji_id": "1356053165874741490", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1440633761074249728", "filename": "06._-Foe_Friend-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 51285382, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633761074249728/06._-Foe_Friend-.wav?ex=69cce43e&is=69cb92be&hm=63539c339a7136d2ff4c06d231249029a66c4bc02a89c9433ec52be53f6233d3&"}, {"id": "1440633762059653262", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 812007, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440631823192428564/1440633762059653262/6.jpg?ex=69cce43e&is=69cb92be&hm=95ca2c02afa1875b4c9fb558feb077b926232438e8d3882c7d2d20155d2601f4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440631823192428564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：原初宿命之战", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
