{"id": "1440627975102922753", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：创世痴愚之主 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主**\n脱离主，直面主，忤逆主。\n你的故事无人知晓，你的记忆与世长存。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"The Blind Idiot Lord\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: The Blind Idiot Lord**\nTo break from the Lord, to stand before the Lord, to defy the Lord.\nYour story is known to none, yet your memory shall forever endure with the world.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:01:14.838000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "Sendflowers", "emoji_id": "1400771545370067118", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1440627975602180117", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1336143, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440627975602180117/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69ccdeda&is=69cb8d5a&hm=c1d81302cf2670c862ace953f46cb461295c01f42d979fdf0382d0027487d580&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440628491476406314", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 虚构集-Fictional Collection-**\n\n在漫长的人类文明中，我们构筑了许多东西。\n关于物质，关于精神，关于生存、爱、硝烟与纷争。\n但那只是造物主梦中不值一提的噪声，和疏于勘破的虚构集。\n\nThroughout the long span of human civilization, we have constructed countless things.\nThere are substance, spirit; there are survival, love, conflict, and war.\nYet, these are but the insignificant noise in the Creator's dream, and a fictional collection that we have been negligent in deciphering.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:03:17.951000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440628484937351208", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1149591, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440628484937351208/1.jpg?ex=69ccdf54&is=69cb8dd4&hm=63f08d7d249a38e24cf0a8b1da8036d34d0f48d0167f23659c641347f93ddc3e&"}, {"id": "1440628485315104929", "filename": "01.-Fictional_Collection-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 33637464, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440628485315104929/01.-Fictional_Collection-.wav?ex=69ccdf54&is=69cb8dd4&hm=6df8293d33e03c48a5b1f10cf9fd79f8e63fcc1a7ae47302733b974578f864ec&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440628560514650245", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 社群行为解构-Deconstruction-**\n\n动物，所有的高等动物，都难以避免地被社群行为所控。\n然而她亲身奔赴死亡，如愿解构真相。\n一名疯狂的、绝世的天才，她宁愿亲手引来毁灭，她恩赐众生免于吞食名为希望的砒霜。\n\nAnimals, all higher animals, are inevitably governed by social behaviors.\nYet she walks toward death herself, and as desired, deconstructs the truth.\nA mad, peerless genius, she would rather bring about destruction with her own hands, granting sentient beings deliverance from consuming the arsenic named Hope.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:03:34.411000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440628560069922906", "filename": "02._-Deconstruction-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 29849678, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440628560069922906/02._-Deconstruction-.wav?ex=69ccdf66&is=69cb8de6&hm=15f6e45545a940cdab120b8b34907aadc222364c04ae7e3b7d5eb255690f1daf&"}, {"id": "1440628560585949184", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1161162, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440628560585949184/2.jpg?ex=69ccdf66&is=69cb8de6&hm=33eac90e7fd2573de51bfc491bd28849ab9e2f343956ec54a76d6e48dfccac14&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440629024119324683", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 通向祂们的小径-The Path to Them-**\n\n通向祂们的小径，远离祂们的小径。\n一切即将分别，一切即将终结，一切即将伊始。\n门扉前的身影自此开始了漫长的等待，等待银钥指引你的归途。\n\nIt's the path to Them; it's the path away from Them.\nAll is about to part, to end, to start.\nThe figure before the Gate has since begun a long wait, awaiting the Silver Key to guide your way home.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:05:24.943000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440629023746297907", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1161311, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629023746297907/3.jpg?ex=69ccdfd4&is=69cb8e54&hm=ce34004686a40c345912046393934312fe4fd4abfe3159e0a99589bd8fabdd58&"}, {"id": "1440629024060866651", "filename": "03._-The_Path_to_Them-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 49142830, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629024060866651/03._-The_Path_to_Them-.wav?ex=69ccdfd4&is=69cb8e54&hm=c0842ac7d0d1d34eae0c6ceb63336b4cd7cae190d559acc190dfa0548b4b8dfe&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440629051659128835", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 成为神-Becoming a God-**\n\n作为那枚独一无二的碎片，成为神很简单。\n那么，代价是什么？\n\nAs that unique Fragment, becoming a god is simple.\nThen, what's the price?", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:05:31.509000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440629050124009502", "filename": "04._-Becoming_a_God-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 32340404, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629050124009502/04._-Becoming_a_God-.wav?ex=69ccdfdb&is=69cb8e5b&hm=e13d72274f7f7fac6f29ec98a8cc28b1cf0939c1ccfa68117b118be4d767d46c&"}, {"id": "1440629051462258742", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1144261, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629051462258742/4.jpg?ex=69ccdfdb&is=69cb8e5b&hm=cbb151bf6866ae47278776e5bbc81bc8ac1cabf2b742987649cd84e25ee8c699&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440629211676151898", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05. 存在主义-Existentialism-**\n\n一切都不再有意义，因此你得以站在这里。\n一切曾经的过往，就是你所定义的全部的意义，所以你站在了这里。\n\nEverything ceases to hold meaning, and thus you stand here.\nAll that has transpired in the past constitutes the entire meaning—as defined by yourself—for you to stand here.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:06:09.660000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1440629211042680852", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1148028, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629211042680852/5.jpg?ex=69cce001&is=69cb8e81&hm=ef918670fd38ed1723f92ecff0da7d585e8b73b219b9f27c937dceb7412963ad&"}, {"id": "1440629211365769257", "filename": "05._-Existentialism-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 44127676, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629211365769257/05._-Existentialism-.wav?ex=69cce001&is=69cb8e81&hm=1fc2a309f4b32d62a063b3c047828afe425d959b8f8000825a1776c80dedd257&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440629423736094720", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06. 无目之瞳-Pupil-less Eye-**\n\n得到、失去、斩断、牺牲。\n英雄付出了全部全部的代价，庇护珍宝的权柄即是祂的报偿。\n\nTo gain, to lose, to sever, to sacrifice.\nThe hero paid every last bit of the price, and the Authorities to shelter treasure is Their recompense.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:07:00.219000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1440629423031193650", "filename": "06._-Pupil-less_Eye-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 30933424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629423031193650/06._-Pupil-less_Eye-.wav?ex=69cce034&is=69cb8eb4&hm=45f01e278d65b356c05b9bf34d2e8c8be92e2daa068684e1080c6c6843305a30&"}, {"id": "1440629423492694079", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1149745, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629423492694079/6.jpg?ex=69cce034&is=69cb8eb4&hm=04ad4404886daf3a6367460345609c963c8863a0a3c4d60ef013a103ef261b1d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440629704217333800", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07. 齑粉-Dust and Ashes-**\n\n世界上最不讲道理的是什么？\n祂没有目的，无关恩怨，不辨善恶。\n祂只想在醒来时把梦境中生出的一切，全都化为齑粉。\n\nWhat is the most irrational thing in the world?\nIt. It has no purpose, bears no grudges, distinguishes no good from evil.\nIt merely wishes, upon awakening, to reduce everything that arose in the dream into dust and ashes.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:08:07.091000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440629703471005746", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1135704, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629703471005746/7.jpg?ex=69cce076&is=69cb8ef6&hm=bd83e8c43e4586181a07febe9dcd4ba14b6eb5327549122c426d0653bfdeb517&"}, {"id": "1440629703831588914", "filename": "07._-Dust_and_Ashes-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 4285378, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629703831588914/07._-Dust_and_Ashes-.mp3?ex=69cce076&is=69cb8ef6&hm=6397aaa43f3004eec3ed75a2daf26f71cd312708c4e0b3ba6c556a53f528f3fc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440629954269151294", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08. 剧幕中场-Intermission-**\n\n休息一下，喘口气吧。\n即使面对的课题是世界末日，也不是每个人都有机会同时面对三位如此重磅级的导师。\n\nTake a break, catch your breath.\nEven if the subject at hand is the apocalypse, not everyone gets the chance to face three such monumental mentors simultaneously.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:09:06.708000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🩷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1440629953292144680", "filename": "08._-Intermission-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 31801828, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629953292144680/08._-Intermission-.wav?ex=69cce0b2&is=69cb8f32&hm=f2309d0bb2ccd99a263f7bd0b66d94f8b2e62a074b088d84b33fcad0b294c087&"}, {"id": "1440629953971486771", "filename": "8.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1153631, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440629953971486771/8.jpg?ex=69cce0b2&is=69cb8f32&hm=79b7f8767c3cdbe071ac6e9902bc1fcfe965cb368ce8c0f06e2fc75f44eef333&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440630240090128545", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09. 终焉凝注-Gaze of the End-**\n\n主看向你，你刺破了主的眼睛。\n\nThe Creator cast you Its Gaze, and you pierced Its eye.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:10:14.853000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440630239557586995", "filename": "9.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1162754, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630239557586995/9.jpg?ex=69cce0f6&is=69cb8f76&hm=21f5aebc928d1a3518304b7993c3ab3a1aa37a3c857ffc9fade7e92e9aa6f805&"}, {"id": "1440630239825760306", "filename": "09._-Gaze_of_the_End-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 23502920, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630239825760306/09._-Gaze_of_the_End-.wav?ex=69cce0f6&is=69cb8f76&hm=5c4fbbbae50c335b4858207cc5146ebd203aa97fc4bf933a14f3b6cb8c2f82b6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440630282813440061", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10. 为平日赴死之人-Die for the Ordinary-**\n\n你知道，你没有在为什么伟大的事情作战。\n为了逃课，为了作业，为了甜点，为了朋友，为了火炉，为了虚度时光。\n你只是一个平凡的，为平日赴死之人。\n\nYou know you are not fighting for anything grand.\nIt's for skipping class, for homework, for desserts, for friends, for the warmth of the hearth, for idling away the hours.\nYou are merely an ordinary person, one who dies for the ordinary day.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:10:25.039000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440630282222047284", "filename": "10.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1156501, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630282222047284/10.jpg?ex=69cce100&is=69cb8f80&hm=3d3be02cbb7872c0a92ca0e35fa7afb3a0c2544ccedd7dc2812cd4787f01d409&"}, {"id": "1440630282574237798", "filename": "10._-Die_for_the_Ordinary-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 7136278, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630282574237798/10._-Die_for_the_Ordinary-.mp3?ex=69cce100&is=69cb8f80&hm=5715a0e02a4fa18afc977a087c8dad64f67ebc5706bcbb5d0c82da29010e2cc8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440630609113387080", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**11. K-0617**\n\n从今往后，你将以守密人的称号，与万万千千的弥萨格师生同在。\n\nHenceforth, you stand as a Keeper among Mythag's many students and scholars.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:11:42.835000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440630608501145712", "filename": "11K-0617.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1135123, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630608501145712/11K-0617.jpg?ex=69cce14e&is=69cb8fce&hm=a80c5edef136706a63f1b21d3ad18e2a65ceb72a8a3e912ef8eca6d458f20eba&"}, {"id": "1440630608849276949", "filename": "11._K-0617.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 32023186, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630608849276949/11._K-0617.wav?ex=69cce14e&is=69cb8fce&hm=0ceba35f58f633a83ba7de9cea4879c8c7ec3e570466d140fb074a80061ebeb4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1440630689186844692", "channel_id": "1440627975102922753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**12. 决心落跑的英雄-The \"Fleeing\" Hero-**\n\n弥萨格有史以来最怯懦的守密人，死在了巨大的幸福之中。\n\nThe most cowardly Keeper in Mythag's history died in utter bliss.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T09:12:01.926000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1440630688620740699", "filename": "12.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1168051, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630688620740699/12.jpg?ex=69cce161&is=69cb8fe1&hm=e70fb2bbb97c14647c77d1616d5ea82405b402d2f71ec67d240fc135fcb96551&"}, {"id": "1440630688901501000", "filename": "12._-The_Fleeing_Hero-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 4552036, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440627975102922753/1440630688901501000/12._-The_Fleeing_Hero-.mp3?ex=69cce161&is=69cb8fe1&hm=7cfccc6737dad35d4d389cef26ae6e2c88ced1d00eb23cd0375ad18f84aba5bb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440627975102922753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：创世痴愚之主", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
